ED_Title: Report of the International Court of Justice
ED_DecisionText:
At its 35nd plenary meeting, on 26 October 2017, the General Assembly took note of the report of the International Court of Justice. 

(See A/72/4, A/71/PV.35)
ED_Disclaimer: The final text of this decision will be contained in document A/72/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
